OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry and cloudy across
OL,6,FShetland with just the odd shower. A
OL,7,Ffew bright spells and showers across
OL,8,FOrkney, showers may become heavy later
OL,9,Fthis afternoon. Strong southeasterly
OL,10,Fwinds easing by the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRather cloudy this evening
OL,13,Fwith showers, possibly heavy at first
OL,14,Facross Orkney. Then becoming drier in
OL,15,Fthe early hours with a few cloud
OL,16,Fbreaks. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
