OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry in the morning.
OL,6,FThickening cloud and some outbreaks of
OL,7,Flight rain will spread north in the
OL,8,Fafternoon, turning drier later.
OL,9,FFurther rain spreading north towards
OL,10,FOrkney by midnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FOvernight
OL,13,Frain clearing away in the morning then
OL,14,Fdry with some hazy sunshine, haar at
OL,15,Ffirst across Shetland, a few showers
OL,16,Fpossible in the evening. Mainly dry
OL,17,Fover the weekend.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
